{"tid":1635650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ONCE狗:BLACKPINK真係好卑鄙 係YOUTUBE賣MV廣告","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:09:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"44d586c1cb84a9eb6f3f7ab056df716eb320f144","tid":1635650,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"TWICE&quot;Feel special&quot;扣掉廣告後實際點閱數<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/oDQ8Gl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FoDQ8Gl&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=e3d48f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/oDQ8Gl</a><br />\n<br />\n以下英翻中大意翻:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.knetizen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TWICE-1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knetizen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FTWICE-1-1.jpg&h=bcad7b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從9月20日到9月26日 該週觀看數:29.1M<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.knetizen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TWICE-2-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knetizen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FTWICE-2-1.jpg&h=579ac037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.knetizen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TWICE-3-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knetizen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FTWICE-3-1.jpg&h=b858ab09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從9月27日至10月3日 該週觀看數:17M<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩週內實際觀看數: 29.1M+17M = 46.1M</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.knetizen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TWICE-4-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knetizen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FTWICE-4-1.png&h=2719b86e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至10月3日爲止，觀看數約77.7M<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告觀看數: 77.7M-46.1M = 31.6M<br />\n概估百分之四十觀看數來自廣告，廣告的效果比預期的要好</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.knetizen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TWICE-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knetizen.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FTWICE-7.jpg&h=a7dd7eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFANCY首日觀看數約40M，自從YouTube首日排除廣告後，<br />\n&quot;Feel special&quot;首日觀看數為14.9M<br />\n<br />\ntheqoo使用者留言:<br />\n<br />\n1.不使用廣告是愚蠢的<br />\n2.一切都結束了，現在Youtube觀看紀錄是場公平的戰鬥了....<br />\n3.買廣告是值得的<br />\n4.買廣告很棒阿<br />\n5.哇...廣告的效益比我想像的要大....40%花錢值得<br />\n6.嗯...差別比我想像的還要大<br />\n7.看看如果不用廣告的46.1M..呵呵，不使用廣告是愚蠢的，但我想知道他們花了多少錢在廣告上<br />\n8.海外知名歌星也使用廣告，買廣告很OK，但不要列入Youtube的紀錄呵呵<br />\n9.廣告效果真好呵呵<br />\n10.廣告的觀看數比我想像的要高，但買廣告沒有什麼不好<br />\n11.我不知道這是什麼，但我知道所有防彈的音樂錄影帶，包括J-HOPE這次從來沒有廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原始討論連結: <a href=\"https://theqoo.net/square/1221186436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheqoo.net%2Fsquare%2F1221186436&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=afbf95bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theqoo.net/square/1221186436</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1570456271.A.1EF.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1570456271.A.1EF.html&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5fa48426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1570456271.A.1EF.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑9人地BP??"},{"pid":"78c8d98c625084628112006cb5cc1a7c2a87b9e2","tid":1635650,"uid":37146,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"唔撚明你想講咩，但feel到你對TWICE有敵意"},{"pid":"2501aa325803dea6191caab02ff84f559b223641","tid":1635650,"uid":138138,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"起碼未無恥到買到破埋紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /